## 5.5 Risk Mitigation

### PLATFORM RISK
Distribute simultaneously: YouTube (primary) + Instagram Reels + Facebook Reels + TikTok + LinkedIn. Never single-platform dependency.

### CPM SEASONALITY
```
Q1 (Jan-Mar)   : Lowest CPM — use for evergreen content and testing
Q2 (Apr-Jun)   : Rising — ramp publishing  
Q3 (Jul-Sep)   : Mid-range — consistent schedule
Q4 (Oct-Dec)   : Peak CPM (+40–75%) — upload best content here
```

### AI CONTENT DISCLOSURE
Disclose AI use on About page and in video description. This is standard practice in 2026 and does not impact monetisation. Quality of analysis matters more than production method.

### DEMONETISATION PREVENTION
```
ALWAYS   : Include financial disclaimer at start and end of every video
ALWAYS   : Cite every data point with on-screen lower-third source attribution
NEVER    : Make specific investment recommendations ("Buy X now")
NEVER    : Use unverified statistics or unsourced claims
NEVER    : Inflammatory titles that trigger policy violations
```

### REGULATORY COMPLIANCE
```
AVOID    : Specific investment advice ("this will 10x")
USE      : Analysis framing ("here is the bull case / bear case / base case")
INCLUDE  : "Past performance does not guarantee future results" in financial content
DISCLOSE : Any affiliate relationships or sponsored segments clearly
```

